        This screen allows you to sign in to the app. How to use:\n\n
        1. Enter your username into the text box. Your username must be at least %d characters long.\n\n
        2. If you\'re an assistant, check the \'%s\' box. If you\'re a person in need of an assistant (assisted person, or AP), leave the checkbox blank.\n\n
