    </string>
    <string name="task_current_helper_text">
        This screen lets you view the current task that you have asked for assistance with.
        Until your task has been accepted by an assistant, this screen will simply display the details you wrote for the task\n
        Once an assistant has accepted your task, their details is displayed near the middle of the screen, including their name and phone number.
        You can press the left call button to initiate a call to your assistant.
        You can also press the speech bubble on the right to begin a text chat session with your assistant.
    </string>

